args: So this is a Halloween party...\n▷Everyone's having so much fun!◁
▷And this spare theater costume is\nperfect for us to jump in on the action!◁
What does one do at a party?\n▷Well, you, um, wander around\nand enjoy talking to people!◁
But you can talk to people at any time.\n▷Well...sure, I guess.◁
What was that voice?\n▷Gyaaa! Laxi, what the heck is that?!◁
▷There's something weird flying around!\nCould this be what we heard?!◁
Look carefully, Mascula. It's not flying—\nit's suspended in the air by a string.\n▷Huh? Hey, you're right!◁
Well, crap! Can't believe you caught on\nto that so fast.
Yep! Mym and Estelle kept saying that all\nkinds of weird and spooooky things rear\ntheir ugly heads on Halloween.
And that sounded to me like a time for\nsome quality prankage! But I guess there's\nno getting one past an android, huh?
Obviously not. Now stop with this\nnonsensical trickery.

No can do, buckaroo! It's HALLOWEEN,
you feel me? 'Tis the season for pranking
until you drop—and then you just keep
on pranking from the floor!
C'mon, you guys should try it out.\nIt'll make Halloween a blast for you!
▷You're nothing if not consistent, Luca.◁\nAgonizingly consistent.
Well, well. I heard some sort of fuss\nhappening, and imagine my complete\nlack of surprise to see Luca involved.
Did you really expect anything less\nfrom him considering the holiday?
Well, we can't let ourselves be outdone by\nthe likes of Luca. Time to prank my sweet\nlittle heart out!
Just so long as it doesn't actually make\nany real trouble for people. Do not take\nthings too far, understand?
(▷Elisanne gave PERMISSION\nfor us to go pranking?!◁)
Right then. Let's all get in some good\nold-fashioned trickery and make this\nHalloween party a real treat!
This is incomprehensible.\n▷Hmm? What's up, Laxi?◁
Say, Laxi. Since we don't do things like\nthis often, do you want to join in?
Well, since Halloween is all about tricks\nand treats, everyone in the Halidom will\nbe going all-out with their pranks.
So you mean EVERYONE will\nbecome like Luca?!
Ha ha! I guess you could put it that way.
Luca is a nuisance enough on his own,\nbut now there will be many of him\nrunning amok...
In other words, the Halidom is currently\nin a state of emergency.
The Halidom will be in utter bedlam if I\ndon't do something. I have to stop all the\npranks right away.
▷Now hold on just a second, Laxi!◁\nDon't you want to protect the Halidom,\nMascula?
Look, there's clearly been some kind of\nmisunderstanding here. This isn't anything\nyou need to worry about.
But if everyone is playing pranks at once...
Mischief is just part of the party!\nIt's a way for us all to have fun.
Everyone will have fun by getting up to\nmischief? This is incomprehensible.
A prank is a bad act. Tricking a person.\nLying to them. Frightening them.
How could the one being pranked be\nhaving fun too?

You are correct that they are not normally
laudable deeds, but they are also not the
wholly bad or evil thing that you are
portraying them to be.
Hmm. I suppose it is a bit difficult to\nexplain when you think about it...
Perhaps a bit of real-time learning\nmight help you understand.
So you want me to conduct a prank?
Exactly! I think it's safe to assume you've\nnever done so, based on your reaction.
Affirmative. I've been pranked,\nbut never done it myself.
I figured as much. In that case, let's get\nyou up to some Halloween mischief!
Exactly! Learn by doing and all that.
You can often understand something by\nlooking at it from a different perspective.
▷Well, I think this is a great idea,\nbecause I've been wanting to know\nmore about pranks for a while now.◁
▷I mean, something Luca likes can't be\nall bad, right?◁
I suppose I am a bit curious, so...okay.

My heart feels funny when I don't
understand something. I don't like it.
I want to understand the meaning
of pranks!
